00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:33.560
 We were lucky that we managed to score a goal 

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:38.080
 At last it was a goal scored after playing a free kick. We often do not shoot at fixed parts of the game ... 

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:40.880
