00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:44.080
 if such a term can be used at all. 

00:02:45.320 --> 00:02:51.800
 I saw a lot of concentration in my players. They've done a lot of hard work today. 

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:55.080
 And maybe that's why we deserved to win. 

